00:20:41.360 --> 00:20:43.720
&gt;&gt; Christian Melgar: I'd first
like to welcome, or thank,

00:20:43.720 --> 00:20:45.470
the Library of Congress.

00:20:45.470 --> 00:20:49.160
It's an honor and both a
