00:20:50.280 --> 00:20:54.510
Four score and seven years
ago, our fathers brought forth,

00:20:54.510 --> 00:20:59.470
upon this continent, a new
nation, conceived in liberty,

00:20:59.470 --> 00:21:04.850
and dedicated to the proposition
that all men are created equal.

00:21:04.850 --> 00:21:08.750
Now we are engaged in a great
civil war, testing whether

00:21:08.750 --> 00:21:14.200
that nation, or any nation so
conceived, can long endure.

00:21:14.200 --> 00:21:17.310
We are met on a great
battlefield of that war,

00:21:17.310 --> 00:21:19.950
and we have come to
dedicate a portion of it,

00:21:19.950 --> 00:21:23.490
as a final resting place
to those who died here,

00:21:23.490 --> 00:21:26.820
and that the nation might live.

00:21:26.820 --> 00:21:29.330
This we may, in all
propriety, do.

00:21:29.330 --> 00:21:31.070
But, in a larger sense,

00:21:31.070 --> 00:21:34.480
we cannot dedicate
we cannot consecrate,

00:21:34.480 --> 00:21:36.790
we cannot hallow this ground.

00:21:36.790 --> 00:21:40.180
The brave men, living and
dead, who struggled here,

00:21:40.180 --> 00:21:45.780
have hallowed it, far above our
poor power to add or detract.

00:21:45.780 --> 00:21:50.150
The world will little note, nor
long remember what we say here;

00:21:50.150 --> 00:21:53.320
while it can remember
what they did here.

00:21:53.320 --> 00:21:56.770
It is rather for us, the
living, to stand here,

00:21:56.770 --> 00:22:00.890
we here be dedicated to the
great task remaining before us,

00:22:00.890 --> 00:22:05.240
that from these honored dead,
we take increased devotion

00:22:05.240 --> 00:22:08.830
to that cause in which they
here gave the last full measure

00:22:08.830 --> 00:22:14.090
of devotion, that we here highly
resolve these dead shall not

00:22:14.090 --> 00:22:18.440
have died in vain; that the
nation shall have a new birth

00:22:18.440 --> 00:22:22.100
of freedom, and that the
government of the people,

00:22:22.100 --> 00:22:28.190
by the people, for the people,
shall not perish from the earth.

00:22:28.190 --> 00:22:29.990
Thank you.

